data.description: Charming 4 bedroom home in the craftsman inspired community of Saddlewood Estates, located in "Way South Austin", just minutes from the best of Downtown and 78704 happenings. Lovely updates include modern laminate wood floors in the living area and stairs and a fresh update to the eat-in kitchen with painted cabinets, updated countertops, and select stainless appliances. Upstairs welcomes you to a bonus living area, perfect for roommates as a 2nd living space, playroom, or home office set up. The primary suite features walk in closet and remodeled modern bathroom with large walk in shower, updated vanity and tile. Secondary bedrooms and a second full bath are adjacent to the primary across the loft for privacy. Laundry is conveniently located upstairs near bedrooms. Located at the end of a private cul-de-sac, the property boasts one of the largest backyards in the community, with fire pit seating area and ample room for a future pool. Updated fixtures/hardware, newer dishwasher and garbage disposal (2023), new fresh paint in the living room (11/2023) and regular HVAC service and pest prevention. A turnkey opportunity with refrigerator, washer and dryer included, this lovely home is priced competitively.
